* What is tiny-make ?

	Creating Makefile is troublesome for me =)
	In my point of view, Linux Makefile seems very useful.
	I hope this tiny-make become tiny version of it.

* Where is tiny-make ?

	you can get it

	git clone git://github.com/morimoto/tiny-make.git

